title: Yadosagashi (House Hunting)
synopsis: A nameless heroine packs up her belongings into a large satchel and heads out of the city. Walking on foot across the countryside, she encounters a strange collection of creepy crawlies and ghostly spirits.
staff: [['Miyazaki, Hayao', ['Director', ' Script', ' Storyboard', ' Key Animation']], ['Yonebayashi, Hiromasa', ['Key Animation']], ['Yasuda, Michiyo', ['Color Design']], ['Yamashita, Akihiko', ['Key Animation']]]
